window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>My heart is broken, my pride shattered to pieces on that altar.</p> <p>He walked away so easily, too easily, and I know none of us will ever forgive him.</p> <p>We have bigger issues to focus on, though, here in Salem.</p> <p>My stalker is becoming more agitated, more violent. I’m constantly looking over my shoulder, chasing after ghosts for answers.</p> <p>Add in my three boyfriends, my evil father and my new sadistic father in law and we are all in for an adventure I’m not sure I want to survive.</p> <p>One thing is for sure, though, making our way out of this, dead or alive is going to be one hell of a Descent.</p>"; 
